        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme &amp;quot;Subsidy for Battery Operated 2-Wheelers&amp;quot; by the Climate Change Department, Gujarat, aims to encourage the use of clean energy vehicles among the youth by offering financial support to students from Class 9th to 12th, as well as college students, for purchasing battery-operated two-wheelers of their choice from GEDA-authorized manufacturers through their dealers. The scheme is designed to reduce pollution, promote renewable energy adoption, and create awareness about sustainable transport among the younger generation.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- **Subsidy Assistance:** Each eligible student receives a subsidy of ₹12,000/- for the purchase of a battery-operated two-wheeler.\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "This scheme is introduced by the Climate Change Department, Gujarat, aims to promote renewable energy and clean transportation by providing a subsidy to students for the purchase of battery-operated two-wheelers from authorized manufacturers.",
        "exclusions_md": "",
        "detailedDescription": [
          {
            "type": "align_justify",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The scheme \"Subsidy for Battery Operated 2-Wheelers\" by the Climate Change Department, Gujarat, aims to encourage the use of clean energy vehicles among the youth by offering financial support to students from Class 9th to 12th, as well as college students, for purchasing battery-operated two-wheelers of their choice from GEDA-authorized manufacturers through their dealers. The scheme is designed to reduce pollution, promote renewable energy adoption, and create awareness about sustainable transport among the younger generation."
                  }
